rows.host: AFTERLIFE ENTERTAINMENT, MAY DAY EVENTS, SUBTLE ASIAN DJS & TRIGGER COLLECTIVE
rows.description:
AFTERLIFE ENTERTAINMENT, MAY DAY EVENTS, SUBTLE ASIAN DJS & TRIGGER COLLECTIVE

PRESENT

MEME LORDS

(EVENT PAGE TO BE UPDATED WITH LOCATION IN APRIL)

We're turning up at a unique event space located near the heart of Los Angeles - and transforming it into a full on decked out RAVE. For this event, we'll be bringing some of the city's top talents, as well as some talent from across the country! 

FEATURING

- DAR L DAR (SADJ)

One of SADJ's newest members! Dar L Dar is no newbie behind the decks - as he seamlessly blends euphoric tracks with heavy hitting trap and dubstep!

https://soundcloud.com/rldar

- MISTRHEE (SADJ)

Mistrhee is no stranger to throwing down for certified talent, as he has performed alongside acts such as Quix, Ookay, Elephante and many more! 

https://soundcloud.com/mistrhee

- AZU (SADJ)

AZU is a Los Angeles-based artist whose music draws on complex synth layering, foley elements from nature, and atmospheric pads, to create beautiful, immersive, and passionate soundscapes. His release 'Weeping Willows' has hit 35,000 plays! Check him out

https://open.spotify.com/album/0C2VDY63anljaz7uB8wicP?highlight=spotify:track:0UhbhRsLwCMkukDrRUEO9y
https://soundcloud.com/musicbyazu

- MIYUKI (SADJ)

Miyuki regularly bends trance and melodic sounds into a beautiful audio experience. She regularly puts out her own releases and takes listeners on a journey.

https://open.spotify.com/artist/3jy26GTtKFUsM26F4bUlwK?si=hUWDhtjYSgWI3n496UdWPw&fbclid=IwAR0KNBnJYCzhPPLU3sHrjWqcPWOAPemDNoixKih_7zLOjm_pFFDoMO1H1wM

- REDUB (SADJ/UNDERGROUND ENTERTAINMENT)

Hailing from Buffalo, NY, Redub brings that style to LA with his entire artillery consisting of heavy dubstep and riddim.

https://soundcloud.com/redub_sounds

- MANA SOUL (SADJ)

Mana Soul is a Wizard from San Francisco, CA. Spinning electronic bass beats, a magical mixture of Dubstep, Trap, House & Future Bass will be sure to get any crowd moving. Directly supported JVNA and SNAILS, Mana Soul will be sure to get your mana recharged!

https://soundcloud.com/manasoul/sets/mixture

- NRG B4B THE GRIMM ACE B4B TRIGGER FINGERZ (MA?WHO & REMIX) (SADJ/TRIGGER COLLECTIVE)

The bass music kings of Trigger Collective are stepping up to throw down the headbanging anthems, exclusive IDs, and never heard before mashups to get the party hype going. Trigger Fingerz (consisting of Ma?Who and Remix) will join The Grimm Ace and NRG to form the Trigger All Star Team to break your neck and tear your heart out. 

https://soundcloud.com/triggercollective

LIMITED PRESALES - $10
TIER ONE TICKETS - $15
TIER TWO TICKETS - $20 
TIER THREE TICKETS/AT THE DOOR - $25
